\textbf{Final remarks:}

\begin{itemize}
\item WS is similar to SRGG, but not projective.
\item PA is similar to HSCM, but projective.
\item The only other known unbiased maximum-entropy model that shares the $(\checkmark,\times)$ signature with the RHG model is the degree-corrected stochastic block model.
\end{itemize}

